OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,FFurther sanctions against Russia are a
OL,7,F"major foreign policy priority" for
OL,8,Fthe Irish presidency of the EU,
OL,9,FForeign Affairs Minister Helen McEntee
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThe minister is in Brussels to attend
OL,13,Fa meeting of EU foreign ministers, the
OL,14,Ffirst meeting of the Foreign Affairs
OL,15,FCouncil (FAC) under Ireland's EU
OL,16,Fpresidency.
OL,18,FMinisters will discuss a range of
OL,19,Fissues including the situations in
OL,20,FUkraine and the Middle East.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,FThey will also have an exchange with
OL,7,Fthe foreign ministers of the Gulf
OL,8,FCooperation Council (GCC) during the
OL,9,Fthird EU-GCC High-Level Forum on
OL,10,FRegional Security and Cooperation.
OL,12,FMs McEntee will also co-host an event
OL,13,Fwith the EU High Representative for
OL,14,FForeign Affairs and Security Policy,
OL,15,FKaja Kallas, which will focus on
OL,16,FUkrainian detainees in the occupied
OL,17,Fterritories in Ukraine.
OL,19,FShe will also attend a meeting of the
OL,20,FPalestine Donor Group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,FMs McEntee said: "I look forward to
OL,7,Fworking closely with High
OL,8,FRepresentative Kallas and our EU
OL,9,Fpartners to secure progress across all
OL,10,Fthe priorities we have set for the
OL,11,Fcouncil over the next six months.
OL,13,F"Ensuring continued support for
OL,14,FUkraine will be central to our work
OL,15,Ffor the next six months.
OL,17,F"We were honoured to host President
OL,18,FZelensky in Dublin on the first day of
OL,19,Four EU presidency.
OL,26,@nD@ROUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,F"It was also important that we begin
OL,7,Four term with an event that highlights
OL,8,Fa key issue for Ukraine and the
OL,9,FUkrainian people.
OL,11,F"During my visit to Ukraine in March,
OL,12,FI saw first-hand the terrible crimes
OL,13,Finflicted upon innocent civilians by
OL,14,FRussian forces at Bucha."
OL,16,FShe added: "It is essential that we
OL,17,Fmaintain our support for Ukraine and
OL,18,Fkeep pressure on Russia.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@YO]xD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,F"As we have seen with Russia's
OL,7,Fcontinued indiscriminate missile and
OL,8,Fdrone attacks on Kyiv and other
OL,9,FUkrainian cities, Moscow continues to
OL,10,Fshow no interest in peace.
OL,12,F"It is clear that our sanctions are
OL,13,Fhaving an impact.
OL,15,F"I have been clear in saying that
OL,16,Ffurther sanctions against Russia are a
OL,17,Fmajor foreign policy priority for the
OL,18,FIrish presidency."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,FThe minister said a "significant
OL,7,Ffocus" of the meetings in Brussels
OL,8,Fwould be the Middle East.
OL,10,FShe said: "The recent exchange of fire
OL,11,Fbetween Iran and the US risks
OL,12,Fundermining the agreement on a
OL,13,Fceasefire and of the ongoing talks
OL,14,Frequired to address the issues that
OL,15,Fremain in the region.
OL,26,@nD@UOUoD@FO]rD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,F"We will meet with our Gulf
OL,7,Fcounterparts to discuss how the
OL,8,FEuropean Union can assist efforts to
OL,9,Fdeescalate the situation which, as we
OL,10,Fall know, has a direct financial
OL,11,Fimpact on European citizens.
OL,13,F"Iran's latest attacks on Kuwait,
OL,14,FBahrain and Jordan are unacceptable,
OL,15,Fas are its attacks on commercial
OL,16,Fshipping in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,F"Freedom of navigation must be upheld,
OL,7,Fin accordance with international law.
OL,8,FAs I emphasised during my recent visit
OL,9,Fto the Gulf, only the hard work of
OL,10,Fdialogue and diplomacy will bring
OL,11,Flasting stability and security to the
OL,12,Fregion."
OL,14,FMs McEntee added: "We will also
OL,15,Fdiscuss the catastrophic situation in
OL,16,FGaza and the West Bank. Conditions
OL,17,Fcontinue to deteriorate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783900129
OL,3,CRussia sanctions are 'priority' for
OL,4,CIrish presidency of EU ` Helen McEntee
OL,6,F"With my counterparts on the council,
OL,7,FI will seek to build consensus around
OL,8,Fa position that addresses the
OL,9,Fconsistent violations of human rights
OL,10,Fand international law by the current
OL,11,FIsraeli government, which undermine
OL,12,Fthe viability of the two-state
OL,13,Fsolution.
OL,15,F"This will include trying to reach an
OL,16,Fagreement at the EU level to address
OL,17,Ftrade with illegal settlements."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@`O]
